@* Pure static HTML — no @rendermode or @code. Renders correctly on both static SSR
   pages (Account/Identity — no Blazor circuit) and interactive pages. Theme state is
   managed entirely by theme.js and the data-bs-theme attribute on <html>. *@
<button type="button" class="nav-link btn btn-link theme-toggle-btn"
        aria-label="Toggle dark mode"
        title="Toggle dark mode"
        onclick="window.toggleTheme()">
    <span class="theme-icon-light">🌙</span>
    <span class="theme-icon-dark">☀️</span>
</button>
